{"tid":1545750,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"［長期置中］Update Telegram! 快","createTime":"2019-09-06T04:36:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T07:50:14.000Z","uid":121869,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4a9186cc4e5dbbfecd9f4bb769014b5ac07444b5","tid":1545750,"uid":121869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T04:36:58.000Z","msg":"Update Telegram! 快！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後改設定：<br />\nSettings &gt;  Privacy and Security &gt; Phone number &gt; Who can find me by my number? &gt; My Contacts <br />\n（之後就只有你 Telegram Contact 上嘅人可以搵到你電話號碼）<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有強烈建議清埋 Telegram Contact：<br />\n     Settings &gt; Privacy and Security &gt; Contacts &gt; Delete Synced Contacts<br />\n（咁樣除咗嗰啲你指名俾佢睇到電話號嘅人之外，其他人都唔可以喺你嘅 Profile 入面睇到你電話號嗎，亦唔可以用電話號碼搵到你）<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外提提大家：<br />\n// 以前已經被搵咗嘅，what's known is known，而家先轉 telegram ID 亦未必可以阻止到繼續被 track。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 覺得有需要嘅可以用新電話號碼（e.g. 儲值咭，記得續期）開新 account。<br />\n2. 唔建議用暫時性電話號碼，減低被 takeover account 嘅風險。真係要用嘅，記得著 2FA。<br />\n3. Last but not least，網上定現實都好，講嘢之前經下大腦。公海甚至人太多嘅 group 即係大庭廣眾，唔係咩都可以隨便講。 //<br />\n<br />\n仲未知發生咩事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/InfoSecOnGround/posts/1206759342837071\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FInfoSecOnGround%2Fposts%2F1206759342837071&d=qjQisgq6tteJ1Wb%2FuF84H51QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=4bf92d12\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/InfoSecOnGround/posts/1206759342837071</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fUUdP1y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfUUdP1y.jpg&h=4290e4e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RkxODUU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRkxODUU.jpg&h=af459a77&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KaLMqzV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKaLMqzV.jpg&h=4fa0882a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n//<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/450882685091411/posts/1217315198448152?sfns=mo//\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F450882685091411%2Fposts%2F1217315198448152%3Fsfns%3Dmo%2F%2F&d=qjQisgq6tteJ1Wb%2FuF84H51QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=abe9a77c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/450882685091411/posts/1217315198448152?sfns=mo//</a>"},{"pid":"75bc5a1bef5c930bb62af224b4c5fd82ac2dde5f","tid":1545750,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T04:37:36.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0718160067d3f57230894113ca266d33851046e5","tid":1545750,"uid":35842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T04:38:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6fc8575ffc9a7a4bf45d1e9c0e3f3cf5de201597","tid":1545750,"uid":35842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T04:38:39.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"cbf25bc05e91752ade25cf40884d6ac26f5611a9","tid":1545750,"uid":35842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T04:38:49.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"c4c8d1fce2b2ed511afac9c345feef8349d0567a","tid":1545750,"uid":35842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-0